03/06/08

Part 1 - 18 min
Before nominations. The boys make a plan of putting up Chelsia against Sharon - Ryan tells Chelsia that she&#039;s going up & will be safe.

Part 2 - 15 min
Josh wants to be Ryans bitch for the week - James/Chelsia talk, she&#039;s pissed that she is going up. - Matt talks to Ryan about noms.

Part 3 - 27 min
Right after the noms. Sharon/Chelsia are up - The girls talk about saving Sharon this week - The housemates get a POV game in the backyard.

Part 4 - 44 min
The house wants Matt out. Nat tells Matt (didn&#039;t get) that the house wants to make a 2 week deal with Ryan if he puts up Matt (which it looks like he will do). Matt talks to Ryan about this plan - Josh talks to Ryan in the HOH, he throws Sharon under the bus and tries to get info from Ryan - Josh/James/Chelsia talk about this plan to get Ryan to put up his best friend in the house in Matt.
